title: Ep. 1117 - Gogi Troubles Everyone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gogi is now staying in Jetha's house. Gogi behaves the same as he does at his place. Jetha finds it very annoying. Jetha goes along with him.

title: Ep. 1118 - Everyone Praises Bhide - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gogi shoots up his gun and the stick is stuck to the roof. Iyer and Jetha wonder how they'll get it down. Jetha shares the same with Bhide, Tarak and everyone praises Bhide for handling all the children during tuition.

title: Ep. 1119 - Champaklal Sits On Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha couldn't sleep in his bed because of Gogi so he sleeps on the couch. Champaklal sit on the couch without seeing Jetha who is sleeping there.

title: Ep. 1120 - Finding Gogi's ID Card - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gogi loses his ID card and gives everyone a hard time about it. Everyone searches everywhere. Finally they gather and decide to search for it inside Gogi's bag. Will they find it there?

title: Ep. 1121 - Jetha Is Upset - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gogi and Tapu return from school after exams and Jetha is worried that he wont be able to handle both Tapu and Gogi. Employees of Gada electronics help Jetha to come up with a plan to keep the kids busy.

title: Ep. 1122 - Cancelled Cricket - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu and his friends play cricket in the society and give everyone a hard time. Everyone gathers and decides to cancel cricket. But will Tapu Sena agree to this?

title: Ep. 1123 - Decision Of The Society - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tarak scolds everyone for acting like children and calling an unofficial meeting to discuss the problem. Everyone decides that the children should not play cricket until the society decides to let them.

title: Ep. 1124 - Daya Defends The Children - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya and the ladies to go to have some street food and run into a lady who talks against the kids. Daya defends the kids and explains what a bliss they are.

title: Ep. 1125 - Iyer Trash Talks Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide and the others wait for Jetha and Tarak so that they can get done with the meeting. Iyer tells everyone not to trust Jetha as he might have gone to have soda with Tarak. Finally, they get to the discussion.

title: Ep. 1126 - Tapu Sena On A Mango Mission - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena break into a grove to pick mangoes. Tapu climbs a tree and starts plucking the mangoes. Will they get out without getting caught?

title: Ep. 1127 - Tapu Sena Gets Caught - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena gets caught after breaking into the Mango grove. They try to talk their way out of trouble. The keeper of the grove asks them to bring their parents. Will they let Gogi go without any trouble?

title: Ep. 1128 - Jetha Handles The Situation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gogi is stuck in the tree and Tapu Sena seeks the society's help to bring back Gogi. Meanwhile, Gogi's parents call Jetha ti check on Gogi. How will Jetha Handle the Situation Now?

title: Ep. 1129 - Jetha And Daya On A Mission - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha and Daya visit the grove to talk to the keeper and bring back Gogi. They try to reason with him to get him back. Will Jetha and Daya bring back Gogi?

title: Ep. 1130 - Anjali's Plan For Iyer And Babita - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anjali comes up with a plan to save Gogi. Everyone plans to dress up Babita and Iyer as a punjabi couple and present them to the keeper so that they can bring back Gogi.

title: Ep. 1131 - Gogi Ruins The Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Finally, everyone convinces the keeper that Babita and Iyer are the real parents of Gogi. The keeper believes them and agrees to let Gogi go.
